sci.crayfis.shramp.util

Class Datestamp

  • java.lang.Object
    • sci.crayfis.shramp.util.Datestamp

  • public final class Datestamp
extends java.lang.Object
    Produces the current date and time as a String, all times are in Pacific Standard. Also gives nanoseconds elapsed from start for sensor timestamps.
